@startuml
title 设备分配与调度（复杂度 O(n³)）

actor 管理员 as admin
participant "设备管理页" as front
participant "Gateway" as gw
participant "zrws-collect" as svc
database "MySQL" as db
queue "RabbitMQ" as mq

== 分配设备 ==
admin -> front: 选择任务 + 设备
front -> gw: POST /api/v1/missions/{id}/devices
gw -> svc: 转发
svc -> db: [SQL] SELECT t_device WHERE status='IDLE'
svc -> svc: 冲突检测（时间/区域/设备三维匹配）
svc -> db: [SQL] INSERT t_mission_device (批量)
svc -> db: [SQL] UPDATE t_device SET status='ASSIGNED'
svc -> mq: 发送 device.assigned
svc --> gw: R<DeviceAssignVO>
gw --> front: 分配成功
front --> admin: UI 更新

== 异常流程 ==
alt 设备冲突
    svc --> gw: 409 同设备同时间段已分配
    gw --> front: 冲突设备列表
    front --> admin: 红色高亮冲突项
else 设备离线
    svc -> db: [SQL] SELECT heartbeat < NOW() - 5min
    svc --> gw: 400 设备不可用
    gw --> front: 提示重新选择
end

@enduml
